{
  "id": "warmonger",
  "name": "Warmonger",
  "titles": "Warmonger",
  "lore": "In seemingly every Legion, there is a cadre of centurions who compete for the honour of leading the spear-tip of any assault. These hardened commanders are much respected for their willingness to heroically throw themselves and their soldiers into the toughest resistance, and are entrusted to prosecute shock assaults which crush a foe in a single action, breaking its lines and leaving its defences in disarray. To these warriors, the informal honorific ‘Warmonger’ is attributed, and any who are marked as such are destined for greatness, rapidly rising in stature and rank, should they survive.",
